Static Code Analysis: How to Pick the Right Tool
The tools that you use to streamline your Salesforce development process are what allow you to deliver the best and most efficient version of your release. 
There are a lot of Static Code Analysis tools available to optimize your code. Major factors that should be considered in your decision making are as follows:
Language Support
Ruleset
Integrations
Cost
